WEBVTT

00:06:28.559 --> 00:06:30.053
It was 10 o'clock.

00:06:31.483 --> 00:06:34.822
None of the leaders showed up.

00:06:36.132 --> 00:06:38.835
That made me angry.

00:06:40.275 --> 00:06:46.679
I was standing, leaning against
Mahatma Gandhi's statue.

00:06:49.839 --> 00:06:54.310
I was emotionally drained,
rather exhausted.

00:06:56.890 --> 00:07:02.375
Then I sat down where 
the food was lying.